Subject: Netwrix Agnet on Netapp Storage Device    [ ref:!00D70091pB.!500Qk0MrqTf:ref ]

TextBody:
Hi Adam,

I have checked internally with my colleagues and unfortunately we do not support Netapp storage devices for the EPP client.

We believe that it runs a proprietary OS called Ontap. It's not a flavor of Linux. Even the filesystem is proprietary.

Please let me know if there is any other information that we can provide, or if we can close this ticket.

Best Regards,
Flaviu Moldovan | Technical Support Engineer
